title: IAA Tonight | Who's the Best Team In the NFL? AND The NBA is Back!!!
description: The Philadelphia Eagles and the Buffalo Bills have been rolling all season, but are they the two best teams in the NFL? LeSean "Shady" McCoy, Leger Douzable and Omar Kelly discuss that and if Dallas should be playing Cooper Rush over Dak Prescott. Plus, the NBA is back! The guys discuss which teams are the best out of their respective conferences and if the Warriors will repeat.
author: smanderville@houseofathlete.com (Leger Douzable, Omar Kelly, LeSean McCoy)
